2002-01-16  Lutz Müller <lutz@users.sourceforge.net>

	Black magic by Marcus Meissner <marcus@jet.franken.de>:

	find . -type f | xargs grep -l gp_debug_printf | xargs perl -pi -e 's/gp_debug_printf\(\s*GP_DEBUG[^,]*,[^,]*,(.*)$/GP_DEBUG(\1/'

