	cameras ignoring delete_all to ...
	* camlibs/sierra/sierra.c: (camera_folder_delete_all): ... here. And 
	update the filesystem - without that, gphoto2 won't be able to 
	fix the behaviour of some cameras (ignoring delete_all).

